ForrestJS Lifecyle Hooks
Here is a comprehensive list of the existing lifecycle hooks.
$START
Services Only
$SETTINGS
Services Only
$INIT_SERVICE(S)
$INIT_FEATURE(S)
$START_SERVICE(S)
$START_FEATURE(S)
$FINISH

